UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'MoMA in New York holds the world''s greatest collection of modern art: Van Gogh''s Starry Night, Warhol, Pollock, and the birth of modernism. The building on 54th St and the sculpture garden are landmarks. Selected for our World 100 as the temple of modern art and a must-visit in Manhattan.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'MoMA – Museum of Modern Art';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'Tate Modern in London occupies the former Bankside Power Station. Turbine Hall installations, Rothko, Warhol, and free permanent collection define it. Selected for our World 100 as the UK''s flagship for modern and contemporary art and one of the world''s most visited galleries.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Tate Modern, London';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Guggenheim Museum in New York is Frank Lloyd Wright''s spiral masterpiece. The building and the collection—Kandinsky, Picasso, contemporary—are inseparable. Selected for our World 100 as the most iconic museum building in America and a landmark of 20th-century architecture.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Guggenheim Museum, New York';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'Guggenheim Bilbao is Frank Gehry''s titanium-clad landmark that transformed the city. Jeff Koons'' Puppy, Richard Serra, and rotating exhibitions. Selected for our World 100 as the museum that defined the “Bilbao effect” and a symbol of architecture as destination.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Guggenheim Bilbao';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'Tate Britain on Millbank holds British art from 1500 to the present: Turner, Pre-Raphaelites, and the Turner Prize. Selected for our World 100 as the home of British art and the counterpart to Tate Modern.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Tate Britain, London';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'Centre Pompidou in Paris is the inside-out building with coloured pipes. The Musée National d''Art Moderne holds Matisse, Dali, Duchamp, and modern masters. Selected for our World 100 as Europe''s leading modern art museum and an architectural icon.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Centre Pompidou, Paris';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Van Gogh Museum in Amsterdam holds the world''s largest collection of Van Gogh: 200 paintings, 500 drawings, including Almond Blossom and Sunflowers. Selected for our World 100 as the definitive Van Gogh experience and a pilgrimage for art lovers.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Van Gogh Museum, Amsterdam';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'Venice Arsenale and Giardini host the Venice Biennale, the world''s most prestigious contemporary art event. National pavilions and curated exhibitions. Selected for our World 100 as the pinnacle of international art biennials and a Venetian institution.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Venice Arsenale & Giardini';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Belvedere in Vienna holds Klimt''s The Kiss and major works by Schiele and Kokoschka in a Baroque palace with gardens. Selected for our World 100 as the home of The Kiss and the heart of Viennese modernism.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Belvedere, Vienna';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'Louisiana Museum of Modern Art north of Copenhagen combines Giacometti, Picasso, Calder, and contemporary art with clifftop views over the Øresund. Selected for our World 100 as the most beautifully sited modern art museum and a Danish cultural icon.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Louisiana Museum of Modern Art';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'Chichu Art Museum on Naoshima is Tadao Ando''s underground building housing Monet''s Water Lilies in natural light. Art, architecture, and island. Selected for our World 100 as the most contemplative and site-specific art experience in Japan.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Chichu Art Museum, Naoshima';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The National Gallery of Art in Washington DC holds the only Leonardo in the Americas and masterpieces by Vermeer, Raphael, and Rembrandt. Free admission. Selected for our World 100 as America''s preeminent public art collection and a national treasure.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'National Gallery of Art, Washington DC';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Art Institute of Chicago holds Seurat''s Sunday on La Grande Jatte, Wood''s American Gothic, and Hopper''s Nighthawks. The building and collection are world-class. Selected for our World 100 as one of the finest encyclopedic art museums in the United States.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Art Institute of Chicago';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'LACMA in Los Angeles is the largest art museum on the US West Coast. Urban Light (lampposts) and broad collections from ancient to contemporary. Selected for our World 100 as the cultural heart of LA and an open-air and indoor landmark.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'LACMA, Los Angeles';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'Louvre Abu Dhabi is Jean Nouvel''s dome with a “rain of light.” Da Vinci, Pissarro, and global art in a narrative of civilisations. Selected for our World 100 as the most ambitious museum project in the Gulf and a bridge between cultures.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Louvre Abu Dhabi';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Palacio de Bellas Artes in Mexico City houses Rivera, Orozco, and Siqueiros murals in an Art Deco marble palace by Alameda Park. Selected for our World 100 as the home of Mexican muralism and one of the world''s most beautiful opera and art halls.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Palacio de Bellas Artes, Mexico City';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Frida Kahlo Museum (Casa Azul) in Coyoacán is the blue house where Frida was born and died. Personal objects, art, and garden. Selected for our World 100 as the most intimate artist house-museum and a pilgrimage for Frida fans.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Frida Kahlo Museum (Casa Azul), Mexico City';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'MASP in São Paulo displays paintings suspended in glass frames along the length of the gallery. Botticelli to Van Gogh on Avenida Paulista. Selected for our World 100 as the most innovative display concept and Brazil''s premier art museum.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'MASP Sao Paulo';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The National Gallery Singapore occupies the former Supreme Court and City Hall. Southeast Asian art from the 19th century to the present. Selected for our World 100 as the definitive museum of Southeast Asian art and a Singapore landmark.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'National Gallery Singapore';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'M+ in West Kowloon is Asia''s largest museum of visual culture. Herzog & de Meuron building opened in 2021. Selected for our World 100 as Hong Kong''s new cultural anchor and a global platform for visual culture.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'M+ Museum, West Kowloon';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Leeum Samsung Museum of Art in Seoul combines traditional Korean art and contemporary works in buildings by Mario Botta, Jean Nouvel, and Rem Koolhaas. Selected for our World 100 as the finest private museum in Korea and a design landmark.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Leeum Samsung Museum of Art';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Tehran Museum of Contemporary Art holds a hidden trove of Western modern art—Warhol, Pollock, Miró—saved since the revolution. Now increasingly on view. Selected for our World 100 as one of the world''s most surprising and politically charged collections.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Tehran Museum of Contemporary Art';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Serpentine Galleries in Hyde Park commission an annual Pavilion by a star architect and show cutting-edge contemporary art. Free. Selected for our World 100 as London''s most dynamic public contemporary art space and a summer ritual.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Serpentine Galleries, London';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Whitechapel Gallery in East London showed Picasso''s Guernica in Britain in 1938. It remains a vital space for contemporary art. Selected for our World 100 as the gallery that brought Guernica to the UK and a pioneer of East End culture.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Whitechapel Gallery, London';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The National Museum in Oslo holds the original Scream by Munch, plus Cézanne, Matisse, and the new building (2022). Selected for our World 100 as the home of The Scream and Norway''s national art collection.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'National Museum, Oslo';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'Fundación Joan Miró on Montjuïc holds the definitive Miró collection in a building that overlooks Barcelona. Selected for our World 100 as the greatest single-artist museum for Miró and a Barcelona landmark.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Fundacio Joan Miro, Barcelona';

UPDATE challenges SET description_en = 'The Albertina in Vienna holds Habsburg graphic arts and major exhibitions: Monet, Modigliani, Klimt. The palace and views add to the experience. Selected for our World 100 as one of the world''s finest print and drawing collections and a Viennese icon.' WHERE category = 'art_galleries' AND title_en = 'Albertina, Vienna';


